<h1>REST API Handbook <a class="github-edit" href="https://github.com/WP-API/docs/edit/master/index.md"><img src="https://developer.wordpress.org/wp-content/plugins/wporg-cli/assets/images/github-mark.svg"> <span>Edit</span></a></h1>


<style> .toc-jump { text-align: right; font-size: 12px; } .page .toc-heading { margin-top: -50px; padding-top: 50px !important; }</style><div class="table-of-contents"><h2>Topics</h2><ul class="items"><li><a href="#why-use-the-wordpress-rest-api">Why use the WordPress REST API</a></li>
<li><a href="#key-concepts">Key Concepts</a>
<ul>
<li><a href="#routes-endpoints">Routes &amp; Endpoints</a></li>
